    • Method Detail

      • transferToWorld

        public int transferToWorld(world.meta.World newWorld)
        will transfer this entity to the given world, updating the meta file and everything. If it fails, it will return the appropriate code and keep the entity in it's current world. There cannot be more than one entity with the same Entity_ID in one world, attempting to move an entity whos ID is also in the new world will fail the attempt
        Parameters:
        newWorld - the new world this entity will exist in
        Returns:
        ont of the CODE_* constants defined above.
